snippet: Shortstop Jimmy Rollins could be headed back to his native Bay Area, agreeing to a minor league contract with the San Francisco Giants that includes an invitation to big league spring training camp....
lead_paragraph: Shortstop Jimmy Rollins could be headed back to his native Bay Area, agreeing to a minor league contract with the San Francisco Giants that includes an invitation to big league spring training camp.

headline.main: Jimmy Rollins Receives Minor League Contract From Giants
headline.print_headline: Jimmy Rollins Receives Minor League Contract From Giants
